Usage: generate_vertical_cell_edge_constraint [-help] {-file <string> | -updateDB } [[-check_m2_only ] | [-check_m2_to_m1_only ]]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-check_m2_only                     # check M2 to M2 pins only in abutted 2
                                   # cells when generating cell edge
                                   # constraints (bool, optional)
-check_m2_to_m1_only               # check M2 to M1 pins only in abutted 2
                                   # cells when generating cell edge
                                   # constraints  (bool, optional)
-file <string>                     # specify file name to output vertical tcl
                                   # constraint (string, optional)
-updateDB                          # update the constraints to DB
                                   # (bool, optional)